{"tid":203950,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港蛋撻圖鑒 & 數據庫","createTime":"2017-04-16T16:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T03:26:12.000Z","uid":41818,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"255b89adba46f6717d3c50115eb3f5d555f7018c","tid":203950,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"百撻圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/nj-eggtarts/img/Egg-Tart-poster_%E7%99%BE%E6%92%BB%E5%9C%96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fnj-eggtarts%2Fimg%2FEgg-Tart-poster_%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%2592%25BB%25E5%259C%2596.jpg&h=ec493732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://feature.nextdigital.com.hk/EggTart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffeature.nextdigital.com.hk%2FEggTart%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d843833d\" target=\"_blank\">https://feature.nextdigital.com.hk/EggTart/</a><br />\n<br />\n【傳承香港地道風味】<br />\n<br />\n歷史悠久嘅蛋撻係香港飲食文化嘅代表之一，所以深度遊資訊平台「壹遊」為香港人做咗以下蛋撻全紀錄企劃，呢幾日假期不妨由此展開尋味旅程！<br />\n<br />\n1. 【百撻圖】<br />\n今日隨《蘋果日報》限量附送，為最齊全的本地蛋撻圖鑑。錯過咗實體版亦可以下載呢個高清版本：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/EggTp2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FEggTp2&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=141e3461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/EggTp2</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 【蛋撻地圖】<br />\n列出十八區靚撻所在地，話你知其實行多兩步，美味就近在咫尺。<br />\n<br />\n3. 【蛋撻數據庫】<br />\n全方位展示近200隻蛋撻資料，包括餅皮厚度 ／ 蛋漿厚度 ／蛋撻直徑 ／ 蛋撻價錢 ／蛋撻重量／蛋漿顏色／出爐時間。立即瀏覽： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/NJEggTart\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FNJEggTart&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9254f32c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/NJEggTart</a><br />\n<br />\n蛋撻大搜查雖然已經出爐，但總有漏網之魚。如果你都有心水靚撻推介，歡迎將餅店名稱、地址、舖面照片與蛋撻價格 inbox 話我哋知，一齊創造最完整嘅香港蛋撻地圖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇落應該幾有用 跟佢嚟揾食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d510877cbfc445aa00e2564d130fad00aa66ff","tid":203950,"uid":72481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"7607ad51b75c7168176211ae94ab7bc3ae48fe76","tid":203950,"uid":1345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"幾有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4616e5a57d599a4bd8ad48d3e5080f3e1682c0d","tid":203950,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a363adf67d82ad5470cf30aab002751a0cd6163a","tid":203950,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"睇到肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d22629f58c2c4783a36601a4e58c12a0588959","tid":203950,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:47:09.000Z","msg":"酥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b8cbe2ad9375938fe5757f853daeec650abde7","tid":203950,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62db83fe85d3c7c5c7dd7068672fdbb786db8d2","tid":203950,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0877f51c18ebeb31e471c8b44af43e7d460cdd07","tid":203950,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b361cad7e240d3835b39d038b051515f80b4698d","tid":203950,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>酥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩皮都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}